<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<title>zài rén hǎi zhōng wǒ yù jiàn le nǐ 迦南985</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zài rén hǎi zhōng wǒ yù jiàn le nǐ, nǐ shì wǒ shēng mìng zhōng de qí jī.
 zhè shì shén de ān pái, zhè shì shén de zhǐ yì. nǐ shì wǒ yī shēng de fú qì.
 cóng cǐ wǒ men qiān shǒu zǒu guò fēng yǔ, zǒu guò rén shēng de sì jì.
 dōu yǒu guò shāng xīn, dōu yǒu guò tàn xī. shì zhǔ de dà ài gǎi biàn le wǒ hé nǐ.
 zài lǐ jiě zhōng, nǐ mò mò fú chí zhe wǒ, zài lǐ jiě zhōng wǒ shēn shēn zhù fú zhe nǐ.
 gèn jìng gèn ài, bǐ cǐ gǔ lì. zhǔ yé sū shì ài de gēn jī.
 zhǔ yé sū shì ài de gēn jī.</lyrics>
</song>